p: Analysis was done using a Hewlett-Packard 5973 with a HP- 5 MS column (30 m × 0.25mm, film thickness 0.25). The column temperature was kept at 60 °C for 3 min and programmed to 220 °C at a rate of 5 °C and kept constant at 220 °C for 5 min. The flow rate of Helium as carrier gas with () MS was taken at 70 e V.
